# 3D Point Cloud Object Labelling

Multi-class point cloud annotation for autonomous systems and 3D AI model training.

## Overview
This repository documents 3D point cloud labelling work — classifying object clusters, applying spatial boundaries, and assigning class labels across dense point cloud datasets. Work supports training of autonomous perception and 3D recognition models.

## Tools Used
- Point cloud annotation tools
- Manual class label assignment
- QA validation pipeline

## Class Schema
| Class ID | Label | Description |
|----------|-------|-------------|
| `OBJ_CLASS_1` | Mechanical Part A | Primary object cluster |
| `OBJ_CLASS_2` | Mechanical Part B | Secondary object cluster |
| `OBJ_CLASS_3` | Background | Non-target points |

## Annotation Pipeline
```
1. Load raw .pcd / .las file
2. Cluster segmentation
3. Class label assignment per cluster
4. Boundary validation
5. QA review & export
```

